      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Interlinea                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Linea di trattini                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   v-ope                  .
