      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      "FATARC     "        to   f-key                  .
           move      w-rip-str-bit-fsn    to   rf-bit-fat-snx         .
