      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-tip-scd-ctr    >    03
                     go to det-tip-scd-900.
           if        rf-zfp-cod-pag
                    (w-det-tip-scd-ctr)   =    zero
                     go to det-tip-scd-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
