      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-tip-scd-401
                     det-tip-scd-402
                     det-tip-scd-403
                     det-tip-scd-404
                     det-tip-scd-405
                     det-tip-scd-406
                     det-tip-scd-407
                     det-tip-scd-408
                     det-tip-scd-409
                     det-tip-scd-410
                     det-tip-scd-411
                     det-tip-scd-412
