      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpg-tip-pag       not  = 01
                     go to det-tip-scd-600.
           go to     det-tip-scd-800.
       det-tip-scd-406.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo scadenza : Solo Incassi Elettronici    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpg-tip-pag       not  = 02
                     go to det-tip-scd-600.
           go to     det-tip-scd-800.
       det-tip-scd-407.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo scadenza : Solo Ri.Ba.                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpg-tip-pag       not  = 03
                     go to det-tip-scd-600.
           go to     det-tip-scd-800.
       det-tip-scd-408.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo scadenza : Solo C.d.O.                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpg-tip-pag       not  = 04
                     go to det-tip-scd-600.
           go to     det-tip-scd-800.
