      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpg-tip-pag       not  = 07
                     go to det-tip-scd-600.
           go to     det-tip-scd-800.
       det-tip-scd-412.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo scadenza : Solo C/C Postali            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpg-tip-pag       not  = 08
                     go to det-tip-scd-600.
           go to     det-tip-scd-800.
       det-tip-scd-413.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
